        AMKBank Online is the Internet banking service provided by AMK Bank, India's premier commercial bank.<br/><br />
        
        2. What is special about Internet banking?<br />
        Internet banking is the most convenient way to bank- anytime, any place, at your convenience.<br /><br />
        
        3. I do not have a PC?<br />
        You can access AMKBank Online from any computer that has connectivity to the Internet. But make sure your computer is Malware free. For more details please Click here.<br /><br />
        
        4. How do I access AMKBank Online?<br />
        You can apply for Internet Bank services at our Registration Page.<br /><br />
        
        5. I do not have an account with AMK Bank?<br />
        You are welcome to open it now via our Registration Page.<br /><br />
        
        9. I want to register for AMKBank Online now. What do I do?<br />
        Fill out the form at our Registration Page and the services will be activated for you within 3 business days.<br /><br />
        
        10. Why are the user name and password so cryptic?<br />
        The user name and password are system generated. OnlineSBI has no control over this process. During your first visit to OnlineSBI, you must mandatorily change your user name and password.<br /><br />
        
        12. Can I change my password?<br />
        Passwords can be changed any time and any number of times. In fact we recommend that your password should be changed periodically to secure access to your account information.<br /><br />
        
        13. What are the good practices for creating a password?<br />
        You are requested to select a word that is not available in an English Dictionary.<br />
        Do not assign your name, your family or vehicle number as your password as it can be easily guessed....<br /><br />
        Rhyming sentences make for very good passwords which can also be remembered easily.<br /><br />
        
        14. What happens if I forget my logon password?<br />
        Click on the 'Forgot password' link in the site to change your current password and set a new one.<br /><br />
        
        15. What happens if I forget my Internet banking username?<br />
        If you forget the Internet banking user name, contact the AMKBank Online Administrators.<br /><br />
        
